OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out at Arthur's Seat
OL,4,Cin Edinburgh
OL,6,FFootage from STV shows firefighters
OL,7,Ftackling flames at the Scottish
OL,8,Flandmark
OL,10,FFirefighters spent the night battling
OL,11,Fa blaze that broke out at Arthur's
OL,12,FSeat in Edinburgh on Sunday.
OL,14,FFour fire engines attended after
OL,15,Fresponding to reports of the fire at
OL,16,F6.40pm, with firefighters seen dousing
OL,17,Fthe flames.
OL,19,FThere were no reported injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
