OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out at Arthur's Seat
OL,4,Cin Edinburgh
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Scottish Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service (SFRS) said: "We
OL,8,Fwere alerted at 6.38 pm on Sunday 19
OL,9,FJuly to reports of a fire in the open
OL,10,Fat Arthur's Seat in Edinburgh.
OL,12,F"Operations Control mobilised four
OL,13,Ffire appliances, and crews are still
OL,14,Fat the scene.
OL,16,F"There are no reported casualties."
OL,18,FIt is the second fire at the Scottish
OL,19,Flandmark in the last three months.
