OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out at Arthur's Seat
OL,4,Cin Edinburgh
OL,6,FIn May, fire crews battled a large
OL,7,Fgrass fire near Arthur's Seat that
OL,8,Fsent a plume of smoke over the city,
OL,9,Fwith no injuries reported.
OL,11,FThe fire on Sunday evening came as
OL,12,FSFRS continued to battle a wildfire in
OL,13,Fthe Cairngorms, which has been burning
OL,14,Fsince Wednesday and now stretches
OL,15,Fnearly four miles.
OL,17,FHelicopters were deployed to the
OL,18,FCairngorms - the UK's largest national
OL,19,Fpark - over the weekend, to douse the
OL,20,Farea with water.
